- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): This category includes papers on algorithms and data structures, and the paper's discussion of quantum algorithms could make it relevant to this category. 
- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science): This category includes papers on logic and its applications in computer science, and the paper's discussion of operator algebras could make it relevant to this category. 
- cs.SC (Symbolic Computation and Formal Verification): This category includes papers on formal methods, verification, and theorem proving, and the paper's discussion of operator algebras could make it relevant to this category as well.
